.Ed
.sp
render a mailbox tree like the following:
.sp
.Bd -literal
0  Inbox 3
1   Archive
2   Drafts
3   Lists
4    example-list-a
5    example-list-b
6   Sent
7   Spam
8   Trash
.Ed
.sp
Other possible trees:
.sp
.Bd -literal
has_sibling = " ┃"
no_sibling = "  "
